title: iPhones Draw Flak Over Battery Life - NewsFactor
text:
Could the battery life of your new iPhone 6s or 6s Plus depend on the luck of the draw? Some recent testing indicates that might be the case. When it was making the phones, Apple subcontracted with two companies to make its new A9 processor, and now that decision could be coming back to haunt the company.
Start the conversation, or Read more at NewsFactor.
